comments:
Abolished 30.9.1885 to become the separate parishes of North Hallow 
    and South Hallow. See also Table 2, note (b).

Created 1894 from the part of the parish of Leigh in Malvern Link 
    Urban District. See also Table 2, note (e).

Created 30.9.1885 from the rural part of the parish of Hallow. 
    See also Table 2, note (f).

Created 30.9.1885 from the part of the parish of Hallow in Worcester 
    Municipal Borough.  
    See also Table 2, note (b).
